    <span class="text-lg md:text-2xl max-w-prose text-center">
      I'm a founding engineer at{' '}
      <a class="text-sky-600" href="https://maven.com" target="_blank">
        Maven
      </a>
      , and I'm interested in education 📚, architecture 🏠, and software engineering🧑‍💻.
    </span>
  </div>
